Description: Modern GTK4 SSH connection manager with split terminals
 SSH Client Manager is a modern, feature-rich SSH client built with GTK4
 and libadwaita. It provides:
  - Split terminals (horizontal and vertical)
  - Tabbed interface with drag-and-drop between panes
  - AES-encrypted credential storage
  - SSH_ASKPASS-based authentication (no expect dependency)
  - Cluster mode for broadcasting commands to all terminals
  - Hierarchical connection grouping
